{"tid":1531222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［831搵失物］去過東涌嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T07:44:01.000Z","uid":285716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"def29f20db1d2e6bef7c5ec2c90b5de804b4de1a","tid":1531222,"uid":285716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:00:28.000Z","msg":"代絲打po：<br />\n<br />\n琴日係喺東涌跌左個卡套，深藍色牛皮卡套(有得打開) 有4張卡係入面。<br />\n<br />\n（類似咁，不過唔係prada）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EExB02o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEExB02o.jpg&h=fd9b80a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有晒個人資料 <br />\naround 7pm左右跌 <br />\n應該係裕東苑巴士站個條街到跌 <br />\n同埋過過一次馬路 <br />\n如果有見過/執到揾 &gt;&gt;&gt; tg: adfldhf<br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8aea00ae309b154aa55e6b320d046518225ac4","tid":1531222,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d0784815db10f5e6547f84ac56f61e4c6262c8","tid":1531222,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 